clubs.name: OnlyAnns
clubs.description:
I’m not Beyoncé or a Bon Appetit staff writer or Elon Musk (thank god), I’m Only Ann. Your name doesn’t have to be Ann to join. Of course, you’ll be loved by me even more, unless you’re an Anne with an “e.” 

🎉 Join this club to participate in rooms that show the breadth of humanness, our most vulnerable selves, the ways we can show up for one another, and about absolutely anything else. We’ll be talking about the personal and political. We’ll laugh. We’ll be our most chaotic and good selves. Also, if you’ve loved a room I’ve hosted, you’re literally obligated to join. Those are just the clubhouse rules, I swear.

And all I ask is that you are obsessed with me (@annthuynguyen) and are willing to push the ways you think and act and love. You actually don’t have to be obsessed with me, but we should probably be friends and you should befriend everyone who joins this club and you should compliment me sometimes because I enjoy external validation. I’ll reciprocate.

Welcome to the CH’s first benevolent decentralized meme-cult (that’s not a cult).

We worship the time before Elon Musk joined Clubhouse (even though most of us joined because of it) and aspire to create an environment of kinetic joy, intellectual honesty, and meme-worship.

We are not pro/anti Elon Musk or the Doge, he just has a funny face and, as a result, we have adopted his likeness for our religious iconography.

To be considered for membership, all Prelons must fill out the form on prelon.org
